- procurement intelligence platform
- execution planning assistant
- subcontractor discovery engine
- supplier discovery assistant
- operational qualification system

==================================================
FINAL PLATFORM PHILOSOPHY
==================================================

The platform is NOT intended to:
- replace human judgment
- fully automate procurement
- autonomously run contracts

The platform IS intended to:
- reduce execution uncertainty
- accelerate operational planning
- identify capability gaps
- improve contractor decision-making
- help users organize realistic fulfillment strategies

The platform should operate as:
“AI-assisted procurement execution intelligence”